summary: Adds npc named Buttcarrots. Nuff said.
descriptionHtml: You can find Buttcarrots in the Four-Shields Inn in Dragon Bridge. No, he cannot be your companion. No, he cannot speak. He is and always will be a useless part of society that [b]CAN NOT [/b]and [b]WILL NOT EVER contribute to anything. [/b][i]Enjoy~[/i]
